  "detailed_description": "In Grid Words you are faced with a 5x5 grid of letter tiles that you must use to create 3, 4, or 5 letter words.  Manipulate the grid by adding new tiles at the sides, which will slide the existing tiles along to create new words.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can see the next 5 tiles that you will be given, so plan ahead and try to make multiple words at the same time.  The more words you make, the higher your score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou begin each game with a limited number of moves.  Play for longer by earning additional moves as your score progresses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour challenge awaits…",
  "about_the_game": "In Grid Words you are faced with a 5x5 grid of letter tiles that you must use to create 3, 4, or 5 letter words.  Manipulate the grid by adding new tiles at the sides, which will slide the existing tiles along to create new words.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can see the next 5 tiles that you will be given, so plan ahead and try to make multiple words at the same time.  The more words you make, the higher your score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou begin each game with a limited number of moves.  Play for longer by earning additional moves as your score progresses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour challenge awaits…",
